data.value:
This is a open source project developed solely to learn and apply the different Chess Algorithms. If you are looking for a serious Chess application to play the Chess, try the Chess Master application.
If you however want to learn about the Chess Programming, then this might be handy application for you. If you have any comments or suggestions, please feel free to send your comments back to me at akbar@syedgakbar.com.
